item.title: LaTeX to HTML
item.description: A chrome extension that will take latex as input and output html that will render like LaTeX.

item.title: About
item.description: Schooling I am currently a senior studying computer science at Utah State University. Projects I have played many instruments but I most enjoyed playing saxophone and Euphonium. I played in a jazz band all through middle school and high school. I am a fan of jaz music with some of my favorite artists being: the Brecker Brothers, Tower of Power, and Charlie Parker. I participated in marching band for 3 years in highschool and this led to a year in the Battalion Drum and Bugle Corps (pronounced `core` ;) ).
